snippet.title: Yuppie Psycho - Executive Edition Trailer
snippet.description:
Executive Edition will update the game with more than 2 hours of new content.
Three new endings. And a lot of new MISTERIOS!

Chat about it on our new Discord Server:
https://discord.gg/2gdK8V2

Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/597760/Yuppie_Psycho/

Nintendo Switch: (Preorder very soon!)
